transcripts.text: We deserve a senator with integrity.  A senator who knows the community he serves.  Lindsey Graham isn't that senator.  After 25 years, he's become another phony politician who will do anything to hold on to power.  Lindsey doesn't work for us.  And it's time to elect someone who will represent us.  An organizer, activist, and leader from our community.  It's time to elect Jamie Harrison for Senate.  MoveOn.org Political Action is responsible for the content of this advertising.
